{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.unnecessarySeqFocusLinter\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">unnecessarySeqFocusLinter</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.Linter\">Linter</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enables the 'unnecessary `<;>`' linter. This will warn whenever the `<;>` tactic combinator\nis used when `;` would work.\n\n```\nexample : True := by apply id <;> trivial\n```\nThe `<;>` is unnecessary here because `apply id` only makes one subgoal.\nPrefer `apply id; trivial` instead.\n\nIn some cases, the `<;>` is syntactically necessary because a single tactic is expected:\n```\nexample : True := by\n  cases () with apply id <;> apply id\n  | unit => trivial\n```\nIn this case, you should use parentheses, as in `(apply id; apply id)`:\n```\nexample : True := by\n  cases () with (apply id; apply id)\n  | unit => trivial\n```\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.unnecessarySeqFocusLinter","kind":"def","line":166,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.unnecessarySeqFocusLinter","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.lean#L166-L187"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTactics\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">markUsedTactics</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">multigoals</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree/Types.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree\">Elab.InfoTree</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.M\">M</a> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Search for tactic executions in the info tree and remove executed tactic syntaxes. ","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTactics","kind":"opaque","line":134,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTactics","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.lean#L134-L162"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTacticsList\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">markUsedTacticsList</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">multigoals</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">trees</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/PersistentArray.html#Lean.PersistentArray\">PersistentArray</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree/Types.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree\">Elab.InfoTree</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.M\">M</a> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Search for tactic executions in the info tree and remove executed tactic syntaxes. ","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTacticsList","kind":"opaque","line":130,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.markUsedTacticsList","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.lean#L130-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.getPath\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">getPath</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree/Types.html#Lean.Elab.Info\">Elab.Info</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/PersistentArray.html#Lean.PersistentArray\">PersistentArray</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree/Types.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree\">Elab.InfoTree</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span c