ted at least once. ","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.getTactics","kind":"opaque","line":109,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.getTactics","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.lean#L109-L115"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.isSeqFocus\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">isSeqFocus</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.SyntaxNodeKind\">SyntaxNodeKind</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"True if this is a `<;>` node in either `tactic` or `conv` classes. ","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.isSeqFocus","kind":"def","line":105,"name":"Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.isSeqFocus","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.lean#L105-L107"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Extra/UnnecessarySeqFocus.html#Lean.Linter.Extra.UnnecessarySeqFocus.M\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Extra</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnnecessarySeqFocus</span>.<span class=\"name\">M</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ω </span